{
  "version": "1.0",
  "id": "macro-web-agent",
  "name": "Web Agent",
  "description": "AI-powered web browsing agent that recursively navigates and interacts with websites to accomplish a goal. Configure the Browser Session node to use WebView (embedded) or Playwright (headless Chromium).",
  "isMacro": true,
  "tags": [
    "macro",
    "web",
    "browser",
    "agent",
    "ai",
    "automation",
    "scrape",
    "playwright"
  ],
  "createdAt": "2026-01-16T00:00:00.000Z",
  "updatedAt": "2026-01-25T00:00:00.000Z",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "input-url",
      "type": "macro_input",
      "position": { "x": 50, "y": 100 },
      "data": {
        "name": "url",
        "inputType": "text",
        "required": true,
        "defaultValue": "https://example.com"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "input-goal",
      "type": "macro_input",
      "position": { "x": 50, "y": 250 },
      "data": {
        "name": "goal",
        "inputType": "text",
        "required": true,
        "defaultValue": "Find and extract the main content from this page"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "input-max-iterations",
      "type": "macro_input",
      "position": { "x": 50, "y": 400 },
      "data": {
        "name": "maxIterations",
        "inputType": "number",
        "required": false,
        "defaultValue": "10"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "browser-session",
      "type": "browser_session",
      "position": { "x": 300, "y": 100 },
      "data": {
        "userAgent": "chrome",
        "sessionMode": "playwright",
        "playwrightUrl": "http://127.0.0.1:8769"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "initial-navigate",
      "type": "browser_control",
      "position": { "x": 550, "y": 100 },
      "data": {
        "action": "goto",
        "selector": "",
        "timeout": 30000
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "init-history-value",
      "type": "logic_block",
      "position": { "x": 300, "y": 400 },
      "data": {
        "code": "\"(no previous actions)\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "init-history",
      "type": "memory",
      "position": { "x": 500, "y": 400 },
      "data": {
        "key": "agent_history",
        "operation": "set"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "loop-start",
      "type": "loop_start",
      "position": { "x": 800, "y": 150 },
      "data": {
        "loopMode": "count",
        "iterations": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "get-page-html",
      "type": "browser_control",
      "position": { "x": 1050, "y": 100 },
      "data": {
        "action": "get_html",
        "selector": "",
        "timeout": 10000
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "read-history",
      "type": "memory",
      "position": { "x": 1050, "y": 300 },
      "data": {
        "key": "agent_history",
        "operation": "get"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "extract-text",
      "type": "browser_extract",
      "position": { "x": 1300, "y": 100 },
      "data": {
        "extractionType": "css_selector",
        "selector": "body",
        "extractTarget": "text",
        "outputFormat": "first",
        "maxLength": 2500
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ai-prompt",
      "type": "template",
      "position": { "x": 1550, "y": 50 },
      "data": {
        "inputCount": 3,
        "inputNames": ["goal", "page_content", "history"],
        "template": "You are a web browsing agent that accomplishes goals by navigating websites.\n\n## YOUR GOAL\n{{goal}}\n\n## CURRENT PAGE CONTENT\n{{page_content}}\n\n## PREVIOUS ACTIONS\n{{history}}\n\n## ACTIONS\n- click: Click element. Selectors: 'a' (first link), 'a:has-text(\"Text\")' (link with text), 'button', '#id'\n- type: Type in input (selector + value)\n- scroll: Scroll page (value = pixels)\n- goto: Go to URL (selector = full URL)\n- done: FINISH and report answer. The 'result' field MUST contain your finding.\n\n## FORMAT\nRespond with ONLY JSON:\n{\"thinking\": \"reasoning\", \"action\": \"click|type|scroll|goto|done\", \"selector\": \"...\", \"value\": \"...\", \"result\": \"your answer here\"}\n\n## CRITICAL RULES\n1. First iteration: You MUST click/scroll/type/goto. Never 'done' on the first attempt.\n2. Later iterations: If you can see the answer in the page content, use 'done' with the answer.\n3. The 'result' field must contain THE SPECIFIC ANSWER (e.g., page title, organization name), never just 'Task completed'.\n4. READ the page content - if it contains what you're looking for, report it with 'done'.\n5. Don't keep clicking if you already have the information needed to answer the goal."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ai-decide",
      "type": "ai_llm",
      "position": { "x": 1900, "y": 150 },
      "data": {
        "systemPrompt": "You are a precise web automation agent. Always respond with valid JSON only. No markdown code blocks, no explanations outside the JSON.",
        "temperature": 0.2,
        "maxTokens": 1000
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "parse-response",
      "type": "logic_block",
      "position": { "x": 2200, "y": 150 },
      "data": {
        "code": "let text = String(input).trim();\nif (text.startsWith('```')) {\n  text = text.replace(/^```(?:json)?\\s*/, '').replace(/\\s*```$/, '');\n}\nreturn JSON.parse(text);"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "extract-isdone",
      "type": "logic_block",
      "position": { "x": 2500, "y": 150 },
      "data": {
        "code": "return input.action == \"done\" ? \"true\" : \"false\";"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "check-done",
      "type": "condition",
      "position": { "x": 2700, "y": 150 },
      "data": {
        "operator": "equals",
        "compareValue": "true"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "extract-action",
      "type": "logic_block",
      "position": { "x": 2750, "y": 300 },
      "data": {
        "code": "return input.action;"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "extract-selector",
      "type": "logic_block",
      "position": { "x": 2750, "y": 450 },
      "data": {
        "code": "return input.selector;"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "extract-value",
      "type": "logic_block",
      "position": { "x": 2750, "y": 600 },
      "data": {
        "code": "return input.value;"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "execute-action",
      "type": "browser_control",
      "position": { "x": 3050, "y": 400 },
      "data": {
        "action": "click",
        "selector": "",
        "timeout": 15000
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "update-history",
      "type": "logic_block",
      "position": { "x": 3350, "y": 300 },
      "data": {
        "code": "return input3 + '\\n' + input2.action + ' on ' + (input2.selector || '');"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "save-history",
      "type": "memory",
      "position": { "x": 3650, "y": 300 },
      "data": {
        "key": "agent_history",
        "operation": "set"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "loop-end",
      "type": "loop_end",
      "position": { "x": 3900, "y": 300 },
      "data": {
        "stopCondition": "equals",
        "stopValue": "true"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "extract-final-result",
      "type": "logic_block",
      "position": { "x": 2750, "y": 0 },
      "data": {
        "code": "return input.result || \"Task completed\";"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "output-result",
      "type": "macro_output",
      "position": { "x": 4150, "y": 50 },
      "data": {
        "name": "result",
        "outputType": "text"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "output-history",
      "type": "macro_output",
      "position": { "x": 4150, "y": 250 },
      "data": {
        "name": "history",
        "outputType": "text"
      }
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {
      "id": "e-session-navigate",
      "source": "browser-session",
      "sourceHandle": "session",
      "target": "initial-navigate",
      "targetHandle": "session"
    },
    {
      "id": "e-url-navigate",
      "source": "input-url",
      "sourceHandle": "value",
      "target": "initial-navigate",
      "targetHandle": "selector"
    },
    {
      "id": "e-maxiter-loop",
      "source": "input-max-iterations",
      "sourceHandle": "value",
      "target": "loop-start",
      "targetHandle": "count"
    },
    {
      "id": "e-initvalue-history",
      "source": "init-history-value",
      "sourceHandle": "output",
      "target": "init-history",
      "targetHandle": "value"
    },
    {
      "id": "e-session-gethtml",
      "source": "browser-session",
      "sourceHandle": "session",
      "target": "get-page-html",
      "targetHandle": "session"
    },
    {
      "id": "e-gethtml-extract",
      "source": "get-page-html",
      "sourceHandle": "result",
      "target": "extract-text",
      "targetHandle": "content"
    },
    {
      "id": "e-goal-prompt",
      "source": "input-goal",
      "sourceHandle": "value",
      "target": "ai-prompt",
      "targetHandle": "input"
    },
    {
      "id": "e-extract-prompt",
      "source": "extract-text",
